Given the circumstances, a decent trap. It occurred to  me too late that moving the  other rook to c8 would have looked less obvious, but no use complaining since he did take the bait. 

(But left me wondering all afternoon/night before he finally did so.[In retrospect this "trap" may have killed me. Don't try this at home, kiddies.])

I guess he never saw it coming.
